<h1>Your order will be available for pickup.</h1>

<p>
Hi <%= @name %>,
</p>
<p>
Thanks for your recent purchase! This email is just to let you know
that your order will be available for pickup at <b><%= @pickup.location %></b> 
on <b><i><%= @pickup.date.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %></i></b> 
from <b><%= @pickup.start.strftime("%I:%M %p") %></b> to <b><%= @pickup.end.strftime("%I:%M %p") %></b>.
</p>
<p>
Remember to have your Stripe receipt ready from when you made your purchase(it will be in your email inbox). 
If you can't make it to the pickup - don't worry! I will keep you up to date on when we can meet up next!
</p>
<% if @pickup.details %>
  <p><b>Additional Details:<br></b><%= @pickup.details %></p>
<% end %>
<p>
Click the link for a map location of the pickup: <a href="<%= @pickup.link %>"><h4>Pickup Location Link</h4></a>
</p>
<p>
See you soon!
</p>
<p>
<b>Jessie Edwards</b><br>
<small><i>Zold Ceramics</i></small><br>
<a href="https://zoldceramics.com"><h3>Click here to visit the shop!</h3></a>
</p>
